      • createArticleList

        public static java.util.ArrayList<Article> createArticleList(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> refinedList)
        Parameters:
        refinedList - The refined ArrayList of strings that is returned by the refineThis() method found in the AuthorBibCreator class.
        Returns:
        Returns an ArrayList of Articles that have been cleaned up and initialized using the strings in the parameter. Pass in a list that's been refined using the refineThis() method and it will return a list of created article objects.
